@node "install" "Usage"

 Select a game from the listview with the currently loaded patch base
 and click on one of the following buttons:

 Start Patching: This patches the currently selected game.
 Start UnPatching: This unpatches the currently selected game. Unpatching
                   can be useful if a patch doesn`t work with a game
 Patch Editor: Allows you to create your own patches. This is only available
               in the full version.
 About: Displays some information about the program 
 Exit: ...

@endnode

@node "MUI" "MUI.readme"

------------------------------------------------------------------------
                        MUI - MagicUserInterface

                              Version 3.8

                  (c) Copyright 1992-97, Stefan Stuntz
------------------------------------------------------------------------

MUI  is  an object oriented system to create and maintain graphical user
interfaces.  From  a programmers point of view, using MUI saves a lot of
time  and  makes life much easier. Thinking about complicated terms like
window resizing or font sensitivity is simply not neccesary.

On  the  other hand, users of MUI based applications have the ability to
customize  nearly every pixel of a programs interface according to their
personal taste.

Please click on the Install-MUI icon to install MUI on your system or to
update from previous versions.  Latest news and support  can be found on
Internet at www.sasg.com.

                              ***********

                               Attention

    If you're still not registered for MUI, check the new and unique
  shareware lottery and great discounts at www.sasg.com. Give it a try!

@endnode

@node "key" "The keyfile"

  The Keyfile is a file which must be copied to devs:. With the keyfile all the
  disabled @{"options" link "option"} are usable and you automatically have the
  full version of the Da Cool Patcher, logical!

  You get the keyfile when you send US$15 or 20DM and the filled in
  @{"Registration form" link "register"} to @{"me" link "autor"}.
 
  It isn`t allowed to spread the keyfile! Your complete adress is encoded
  and saved in the keyfile. Spreaded keyfiles are an act of software piracy!

@endnode

@node "wasmacht" "Introduction"

  With the help of dA cOOL pATCHER (DCP) you can patch your
  favourite games/programs for your personal needings. For example
  remove nervy copy protections, set unlimited lifes or
  weapons and alot more.

  DCP comes with over 150 predefined patches which you can
  apply to your games easily.

  You can also unpatch patched games. 

  DCP is able to patch files and disks. So 'NDOS' games are no
  problem for DCP!

@endnode

